STEP 4 — SPLUNK TRACE INTEGRATION

Implement splunkTraceParser.ts.

Responsibilities:

• query Splunk REST API  
• retrieve distributed trace flows  
• map traceId to services  

Return trace structure:

{
 traceId:"",
 services:[]
}

Mock the API response for now but design the code so it can call Splunk REST endpoints later.

--------------------------------------------------

STEP 5 — AST CODE SCANNER

Implement:

javaAstScanner.ts
nodeAstScanner.ts

Responsibilities

Scan source code to extract:

REST endpoints  
external API calls  
service dependencies  

Examples

Java

@RestController
@GetMapping("/payments")

Node

app.get("/orders")

Return metadata:

{
 service:"",
 endpoints:[],
 dependencies:[]
}

Use JavaParser style parsing for Java and Babel parser for Node.

--------------------------------------------------

